ATTR CExpr [ jvBuiltin: PP_Doc | | ]

SEM CExpr
  | Let         body        .   jvBuiltin   =   empty

SEM CBind
  | Bind        expr        .   jvBuiltin   =   empty

SEM CPatBind
  | Bind        offset      .   jvBuiltin   =   empty

SEM CAlt
  | Alt         expr        .   jvBuiltin   =   empty
